{"tid":2003120,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"再出發大聯盟被指偷片　新版 MV 刪獨立音樂場地畫面","createTime":"2020-05-05T14:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T16:15:26.000Z","uid":49669,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"963aa1a7e0b12dc3d1e4b3f65a336804cd5d3acc","tid":2003120,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200505-2120copy_4Y25m_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200505-2120copy_4Y25m_1200x0.png&h=ade911a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由全國政協副主席董建華和梁振英牽頭的「香港再出發大聯盟」今日成立，同日公開了主題曲《再出發》，但 MV 被指偷用了本地獨立音樂場地 Hidden Agenda：This Town Needs（TTN）的畫面。大聯盟強調影片不存在侵權問題，但晚上再上傳的版本已將 TTN 有關畫面刪去。<br />\n<br />\n今日較早前聯盟公開了主題曲《再出發》，由周柏豪、菊梓喬、胡鴻鈞、鄭俊弘、泳兒以及許靖韻演唱，鍾鎮濤編曲、簡嘉明填詞、葉澍暉作曲。 MV 中出現了 TTN 的畫面。TTN 隨即在 Facebook 發布 MV 截圖並寫道：「我地响港共旗下既維穩組織-香港再出發大聯盟既盟歌入邊發現呢一幕」。TNN 表示「偷片」事小，但被「香港再出發大聯盟」所用就另當別論。TTN 批評指：「唔講以為甘多年來香港政府對 Hidden Agenda 既打壓係幫左我地甘，唔講以為林鄭做就香港獨立音樂場地既掘起甘，要用既用番林鄭引以為傲既西狗文化區，我地呢啲游牧民族係你地政府眼中只係微塵一篤，唔配同你地再出發￼￼」。<br />\n<br />\n香港再出發大聯盟回應傳媒查詢時，強調不存在任何侵犯版權問題，指主題歌《再出發》裡面的所有視頻、音樂均為「大聯盟」本身創作或已購買版權。<br />\n<br />\nTTN 前身為 hidden agenda，今年 2月宣布結業，指多場演出全數取消、改期，在「康復香港無期」等種種不明朗狀況之下，實在無辦法繼續營運。Hidden Agenda 被喻作「獨立音樂界紅館」，2017年遭入境處放蛇，並以「事前無申請工作簽證」為由，拘捕當晚演出的英國樂隊「This Town Needs Guns」。幾個月後，HA 宣佈交還單位。2018年，Hidden Agenda 易名「This Town Needs」正式復業，至今已有兩年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%81%B7%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88-mv-%E5%88%AA%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2/?fbclid=IwAR1g90Zmcj9INX6EU-sc3sj8i7PCT8MIRR8z7pQsrv3jhOCT5HxEAasVRbg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2589%2588-mv-%25E5%2588%25AA%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%259D%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1g90Zmcj9INX6EU-sc3sj8i7PCT8MIRR8z7pQsrv3jhOCT5HxEAasVRbg&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ee8c2b1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2581%25B7%25E7%2589%2587-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2589%2588-mv-%25E5%2588%25AA%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%259D%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1g90Zmcj9INX6EU-sc3sj8i7PCT8MIRR8z7pQsrv3jhOCT5HxEAasVRbg&h=8eded5ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%81%B7%E7%89%87-%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88-mv-%E5%88%AA%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%9C%B0%E7%95%AB%E9%9D%A2/?fbclid=IwAR1g90Zmcj9INX6EU-sc3sj8i7PCT8MIRR8z7pQsrv3jhOCT5HxEAasVRbg</a>"},{"pid":"2504913b0770ae2237c4ee7e6c05d3dc50b1ed2f","tid":2003120,"uid":49669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"入黎負評+Report啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v0KyQxt7qlg&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dv0KyQxt7qlg%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=cf20abf8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v0KyQxt7qlg&amp;feature=emb_logo</a>"},{"pid":"7df24c97919ffa59a09336b9476b3c5b4548113d","tid":2003120,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2504913b0770ae2237c4ee7e6c05d3dc50b1ed2f","tid":2003120,"uid":49669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-0